                    <span>I know so many people personally and in business that walk around with their eyes on the ground trying to figure out how to get what they want.  RoAne makes it very clear; the answer's right in front of you!  Success is a true "can't see the forest through the trees" scenario.  How To Create Your Own Luck helps you smack right into one of those trees and clear your blurred vision of hopelessness.  It's a great book for young entrepreneurs like me!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Lucky Step #1: Read This Book!</div>
