                    <span>If you've ever wondered how you could bring more luck into your life, Susan RoAne has the perfect answer. With her trademark humor, she distills the stories of real people who turned serendipity and You Never Know opportunities into success. She provides insights and a game plan so we can do the same. Create your own good luck by reading this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Effortlessly reaching your goals while embracing life</div>
